name: 3.Model Training and Evaluation

Model Used:

In this analysis, we employed the Random Forest classifier model. Given the dataset's pronounced imbalance, we incorporated class-balanced features to address this challenge effectively. To ensure robust evaluation, we implemented a 5-fold cross-validation approach. The subsequent sections provide a comprehensive overview of the model's performance on both training and testing datasets.
